## Twabatuma mukufunda abashilika besu ukwishiba ukulwa no lupanga cilya batila 'fikishi beneshi' bonse 8000 bafwile ukwisa bwangubwangu uleke tupokololeko abantu besu mu Jujumo, Damama na Kukuwe pantu bonse balibasesha mu mishi yabo bambi babatwala kwa linso na mona; bambi papita imilundu ikumi ukufuma kumyabo ku mishi.
